videos.description: Late in overtime, Rutgers G Corey Sanders tries for a 3-pointer and doesn't connect. Sanders gets the rebound and goes back to 3-point range, launches a shot and makes it as the buzzer sounds to send the game to a second overtime.
videos.headline: Rutgers' Sanders fixes his mistake, sends game to 2OT
